{
  "stem": "22889.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Samuel Mendler, Jacob Mendler, Morris Mendler, Willie Mendler, Emil Mendler, Max Mendler, Regina Mendler, Helena Mendler, Anda Mendler, Frydka Mendler, Gustav Korn, and Mala Korn, Anna Korn, Leon Korn, my brother, Gershon Reibeisen, my grandfather, Elayza Reibeisen, my father, Mundek Reibeisen, my uncle, Nisim-- Nusim Reibeisen, Yankel Reibeisen, Faiga Reibeisen, Balcia Reibeisen, Ruzia Reibeisen, Dora Reibeisen, Hania Reibeisen, Henia Reibeisen, Hermina Reibeisen.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was my immediate family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But all together, my cousins and my uncles and my distant cousins, second cousins, 72 people, I figure out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how many more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, you were very young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You probably didn't even know half the family--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I knew exact-- what I-- what I knew of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I'm sure there must be more, which I didn't even know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't-- Our family, we were very close to each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was always a family affair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no secret.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I knew exactly where my father kept the money and so forth, on everything, you know, because we were in business.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For instance, now they're coming out with the money in-- in-- Switzerland",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew I had an uncle, Neugroschel, on the outside of Vienna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he kept all the money down there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But of course, he is a relation, too, you know, left over?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, this cousin, while he was there, one of the judges in the Nuremberg trial, he's from the Neugroschel family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sure, if he's alive, he's still going to apply, maybe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I hope so, anyhow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I have my affidavit in hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wait.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I register.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why I couldn't go to Poland with my friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I had to go to the Polish embassy to sign the application coming to United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
